  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Grill the peanuts until lightly charred, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add garlic and green onions to the hot pan; stir-fry for about 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Drain any excess moisture from the peanuts if needed.",
    "Mix in coconut milk, fish sauce, soy sauce, white pepper powder, sugar-free sugar, and fish starch. Stir well until everything is well combined and thickened.",
    "Remove from heat and serve hot over rice or noodles."
